SUMMARY:Bug Hunter and The Narcissist Cookbook
DTSTAMP:20260401T044545Z
DTSTART:20260521T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Doors: 6:30 PM\nTickets: https://www.ticketweb.com/event/bug-hu
	nter-and-the-narcissist-chop-suey-tickets/14150094?REFID=clientsitewp\nVen
