	our website to view the Arena Guide with Bag Policy and Prohibited Items l
	ist.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/seattle-storm-vs-phoenix-mercury-seat
	tle-washington-06-03-2026/event/0F00646A89224C58\n\nFrom Climate Pledge Ar
